    public final class SelectItemDialog

    A modal dialog that displays a list of items in a combo box for user selection. It is intended for internal use by the SwingUI.

                           String prompt,
                           List<T> items,
                           int initialSelectedIdx)
        Show the SelectItemDialog.
        Type Parameters:
        T - type of items
        Parameters:
        header - header text
        prompt - prompt text
        items - items to show in a combo box
        initialSelectedIdx - item index to select when the dialog is shown, or -1 for no selection
        Returns:
